title: EUR/USD reverses early declines, climbs back over 1.04

US Consumer Price Index (CPI) numbers came in above forecasts across the board, but markets are absorbing the hit quickly and moving on to fresher headlines.

The key dataprint on Thursday will be US Producer Price Index (PPI) inflation, as European economic data takes a backseat this week.
